data.title: Nice Upgrade from Panda Express
data.text: We don't have this chain where I live but wish we did.  We eat a lot of Panda Express but this is much better (and a little more expensive but worth it.) Favorite dish was Mongolian Beef.  Tucked behind some other strip mall businesses it's a bit hard to find.  Would visit again when in the area for this quality Asian fast food.
